} Entity Endpoint /api/v2/articles/ [doc_id] Example: /api/v2/articles/7990 URL Params Note: All URL params are optional. Call one or more specific body field elements by ID After the article ID, enter a forward slash followed by one or more comma-separated element IDs. When this parameter is used, the contents of the body field will only return the specified element(s). If the specified element(s) do not exist in the article, the body field will be empty. Example: /api/v2/articles/7990/element_id1,element_id2 Entity Sample Response {
